   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Petearpsenesis, son of Lykos, about 40 years old, with a scar on the small finger of his left hand. Taorothis, about 40 years old, with a scar near her left shin. Pyrrhos, son of Neoteros, about 30 years old, with a scar on his forehead beneath the hair, on the right side. Eudaimonis, daughter of Herodes, about 50 years old, with a scar near her right calf.</ab>
         </div>
